{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <i>tiny</i> robot with a <strong>BIG</strong> heart!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a mysterious explosion rains golden cogs and trash down from the sky, <strong>Buddy and Bag Boy</strong>\u00a0must work together to restore each village and uncover the secret behind the blast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308940/extras/title1.png?t=1731597393\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308940/extras/Buddy_Jump.gif?t=1731597393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a familiar world from a fresh perspective, hopping over everyday objects, solving puzzles, and collecting hidden treasures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308940/extras/Characters.png?t=1731597393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet a colorful cast of robots made from everyday items, and uncover their heartfelt stories. Solve puzzles, reunite secret lovers, and help those in need. Who knows what surprises await!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308940/extras/titleclean.png?t=1731597393\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308940/extras/Buddy_Plant.gif?t=1731597393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make a real difference by recycling trash, scrubbing goop, and repairing broken machinery. Each action contributes to a cleaner, brighter world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embrace the joy of making a difference on this unforgettable adventure.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731597393","background_raw":"https://